static TenderReport::get (  )  [static]

Generate a tender report

Returns:
[string] receipt contents
This method can be overriden by subclasses to create alternate tender reports. When called, this function will use whichever module is listed in the configuration setting "TenderReportMod". If nothing has been selected, the "DefaultTenderReport" module is used.

Reimplemented in DefaultTenderReport, HarvestNewTenderReport, WfcTenderReport, and YPSITenderReport.
